        <h2>Project Overview</h2>
        <p>The goal of this project was to develop a website for a tenant placement service. A backend infrastructure had already been created before I began my involvement, providing a foundation to design a site to market the product. The MVP was to be a fairly small site focusing on highlighting the benefits of said product.</p>
        <p>I first began by setting out to create a definitive style guide. I was able to reference the backend application to create consistency with color choices and typography.</p>
