        <p>With the design set, I then began to develop the site using <a href="https://middlemanapp.com">Middleman</a>, a static site generator. Seeing as it site was not going to have any dynamic data requiring the use of a CMS, I felt a static site would be much more efficient to develop and deploy, while also providing quick load times.</p>
