        <h3>Concluding Thoughts</h3>
        <p>Working directly with the founder on this project made the experience extremely enjoyable. I was able to establish a creative dynamic leading to a collaborative design experience. Because I decided to develop the site myself, it forced me to approach my designs from a different lens than what I was used to. I not only had to come with an appropriate design but be conscious on how to develop those elements. It gave me a newfound appreciation for the development cycle and helped improve my development chops.</p>
